[supply-lines] Supply Line Rough-In (notstarted)
Run PEX or copper supply lines to kitchen, bathroom, and water heater locations.
Install shut-off valves at each fixture location.
---
[drain-lines] Drain & Vent Rough-In (notstarted)
Install DWV (drain-waste-vent) piping for sink, shower, and toilet.
Ensure proper slope (1/4" per foot) and vent through the roof.
---
[water-heater] Water Heater Installation (notstarted)
Install a tankless or compact tank water heater and connect supply/gas lines.
-> supply-lines
> Tankless saves space — ideal for tiny homes. Consider point-of-use units.
